# ================= NoKLock public repo — secret-proof .gitignore =================
# Belt-and-braces. Even if the private dev tree is re-synced into this folder,
# NONE of the following can ever be committed. Real secrets live only on the
# server and in the private monorepo. This public repo is source + the public
# build config (apps/web/.env.public) so the app is reproducible & auditable.

# --- backend / server: NEVER publish (the off-chain trust root) ---
server-form-b/
server-form-a/

# --- env / secrets (allow ONLY the public + example configs) ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.public
!.env.example

# --- private keys / mnemonics / keystores ---
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
*.jks
*.keystore
keystore.properties
keystores/
secrets/
*mnemonic*
*seed*.txt
*.secret
secrets.*

# --- databases (may hold user / licence PII) ---
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.db
**/data/*.sqlite*

# --- dependencies / build output ---
node_modules/
dist/
build/
.vite/
coverage/

# --- foundry build artifacts (if contracts are added later) ---
contracts/out/
contracts/cache/
contracts/broadcast/
contracts/foundry.lock

# --- backups / archives / logs / editor & tooling junk ---
backups/
_backup-*/
*.tgz
*.zip
*.log
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.bak*
kca0.xml
